OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FIt is unlikely that all the
OL,8,Frecommendations of the Renewable Heat
OL,9,FIncentive (RHI) Inquiry will be fully
OL,10,Fimplemented, an Audit Office report
OL,11,Fhas found.
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland's auditor general
OL,14,FDorinnia Carville described the lack
OL,15,Fof progress four years after the
OL,16,Finquiry reported as "concerning".
