OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FShe also highlighted that in some
OL,8,Fareas examined by the inquiry, such as
OL,9,Frecord keeping, the performance of
OL,10,FStormont departments has actually got
OL,11,Fworse.
OL,13,FThe RHI scheme, set up in Northern
OL,14,FIreland in 2012, incentivised
OL,15,Fbusinesses and farmers to switch to
OL,16,Fthe eco-friendly boilers by paying
OL,17,Fthem a subsidy for the wood pellet
OL,18,Ffuel needed to run them.
