OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FBut mistakes in its designs saw the
OL,8,Fsubsidy rates set higher than the
OL,9,Factual cost of the wood pellets, with
OL,10,Fapplicants finding themselves able to
OL,11,Fburn to earn.
OL,13,FWith Stormont facing an overspend bill
OL,14,Fof hundreds of millions of pounds,
OL,15,Fcost-control steps were taken in 2019.
OL,17,FIn 2020, a public inquiry identified a
OL,18,Fmultiplicity of mistakes in the
OL,19,Frunning of the scheme.
