OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FThe inquiry, chaired by retired judge
OL,8,FSir Patrick Coghlin, produced a 656-
OL,9,Fpage, three-volume report containing
OL,10,F319 findings and making a number of
OL,11,Frecommendations.
OL,13,FMs Carville's report found that, out
OL,14,Fof 42 recommendations, a total of 26
OL,15,Fhave been implemented, with a further
OL,16,F11 likely to be implemented in the
OL,17,Ffuture.
