OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FIt said that, while departments have
OL,8,F"undoubtedly made progress" since a
OL,9,Fprevious audit report, the overall
OL,10,Fpace of implementation has been slow.
OL,12,FIt said 16 recommendations have still
OL,13,Fnot been fully implemented.
OL,15,FFurthermore, it said that planned
OL,16,Factions by departments in relation to
OL,17,Ffive recommendations are unlikely to
OL,18,Ffully address the inquiry's concerns.
OL,20,FIn the case of two of these, the
OL,21,Fstatus has regressed since 2022.
