OL,7,FParticular concerns were raised with
OL,8,Fregards to records management, with
OL,9,Fthe overall position of the 'record
OL,10,Fkeeping' theme having regressed since
OL,11,F2022, the auditor said.
OL,13,FAdditionally, the report notes
OL,14,Fdifficulties encountered by the
OL,15,Fauditor in securing timely access to
OL,16,Fadequate records as part of its review.
