OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FIt said that despite the Department of
OL,8,FFinance having published a progress
OL,9,Freport in March 2024, a complete and
OL,10,Freadily accessible audit trail of the
OL,11,Frelevant documentation to support this
OL,12,Fassessment was "largely absent" when
OL,13,Frequested.
OL,15,FMs Carville said: "Considering the
OL,16,Fseriousness of the RHI Inquiry's
OL,17,Ffindings and the level of public
OL,18,Finterest, the lack of progress is
OL,19,Fconcerning.
