OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,F"The inquiry's findings demonstrated
OL,8,Fthe significant learning and
OL,9,Fimprovement that was needed from the
OL,10,FNI Civil Service to rebuild public
OL,11,Fconfidence.
OL,13,F"Four years on, a significant number
OL,14,Fof recommendations have yet to be
OL,15,Ffully implemented and, in our
OL,16,Fassessment, several are unlikely to be
OL,17,Fproperly addressed by the actions
OL,18,Fcurrently planned."
OL,20,F"Appropriate oversight will be vital
OL,21,Fgoing forward."
