OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,FShe added: "An Executive sub-
OL,8,Fcommittee, previously established for
OL,9,Fthis purpose, last met in December
OL,10,F2020 and no equivalent sub-committee
OL,11,Fhas been constituted since the
OL,12,FExecutive was restored earlier this
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,F"As a result, this report calls on the
OL,16,FDepartment of Finance to explore
OL,17,Fsuitable oversight mechanisms for the
OL,18,Fremaining recommendations ` both those
OL,19,Fof the inquiry and those in today's
OL,20,Freport."
