OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Department of
OL,8,FFinance said: "Considerable work has
OL,9,Fbeen done on reforms recommended by
OL,10,Fthe Renewable Heat Incentive Inquiry.
OL,12,F"This is reflected in 26
OL,13,Frecommendations having been
OL,14,Fimplemented with a further 11 to be
OL,15,Fimplemented in the near future.
OL,17,F"The Department of Finance has
OL,18,Fpublished an update of the
OL,19,Fimplementation of the recommendations
OL,20,Fof the RHI Inquiry on the departmental
OL,21,Fwebsite.
