OL,7,F"This progress was made within the
OL,8,Fcontext of a global pandemic, absence
OL,9,Fof functioning institutions and
OL,10,Fextreme budget pressures."
OL,12,FThe SDLP's Stormont leader Matthew
OL,13,FO'Toole said the report paints a
OL,14,F"bleak picture" for Stormont.
OL,16,FHe said: "Particularly shocking is the
OL,17,Ffact that an Executive sub-committee
OL,18,Fset up to implement the review's
OL,19,Ffindings has not met in four years.
