OL,3,CUnlikely that all RHI Inquiry
OL,4,Crecommendations will be implemented,
OL,5,Cauditor finds
OL,7,F"The fiasco over record keeping and
OL,8,FCovid seems to point to a Stormont
OL,9,Fregime at both political and official
OL,10,Flevel that is simply unwilling to
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,F"The DUP may have been the party most
OL,14,Fculpable for the RHI fiasco in the
OL,15,Ffirst place, but this report casts
OL,16,FSinn Fein in a damning light.
OL,18,F"They still maintain that they were
OL,19,Fright to collapse government over RHI
OL,20,Fin 2017, a decision which led to three
OL,21,Fyears of political chaos.
