OL,7,F"But since 2020, successive finance
OL,8,Fministers in charge of pushing through
OL,9,Fpost-RHI reforms have been Sinn Fein
OL,10,Fones ` and this report illustrates
OL,11,Fthat they simply haven't bothered."
OL,13,FHe added: "We are now nearly half a
OL,14,Fdecade into the new decade that was
OL,15,Fmuch heralded in 2020, but neither the
OL,16,FExecutive parties nor the Civil
OL,17,FService leadership appear to be
OL,18,Fserious about a new approach."
